The paper discusses the design and analysis of IoT systems, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of tools for analysis suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems (cs.SY). The analysis of communication soundness also suggests a focus on security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of a specification language and term-algebra suggests a focus on programming languages (cs.PL).
